  "text": "ERdj5 and PDI genes were purchased from the American Type Culture Collection in pCMV-Sport6ccdB and pBluescript SKϪ vectors, respectively. The PDI gene was subcloned in the pCMV-Sport6ccdB vector using NotI and KpnI restriction sites. NDV F and HN genes were inserted into pSVL and pCAGGS expression vectors as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
